[normal]Executive summary:[bold]&#xa0;[bold]In my capacity as both Purchasing Director of Regain Polymers Limited and Vice Chair of the British Plastics Federation Recycling Group, I make the following written submission to the Environmental Audit Committee’s inquiry on Plastic Bags.
